apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji depicts a woman with a medium-dark skin tone in dynamic motion, her body angled as she energetically bounces a vibrant, primary-colored ball. Apple's signature glossy 3D shading imbues the figure with a sense of playful realism and spirited activity, highlighted by smooth gradients and soft, rounded edges. She appears focused and joyful, embodying themes of recreation, exercise, and lighthearted fun in digital conversations.
